#####################################################
#               INSTALL                             #
#####################################################
BINARY INSTALLATION:

To install ABCMaster, choose a directory and uncompress the distribution files there.
For example, /home/abcmaster

>cd /home/abcmaster
>unzip master-bin.zip


SOURCE INSTALLATION:

System Requirements:

JDK1.5-compatible java source code compiler(http://java.sun.com/javase/)
and apache-ant(http://ant.apache.org/)


>cd /home/abcmaster
>unzip master-src.zip
>ant

If successed, a sub directory of "dist" will be created under /home/abcmaster.


